<title>Nang Vawp Inla, Pui Zelin</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei suonteu kawma chung Pathien A thuguot chu,
 Nupan leh pumkhat a hung uma;
 A suonteu sietlei chung luoh dima,
 Ganhing leh thilsiem chunga leng chang di'n;
 Chungnunna chu A pie tai.

[V2]
 Aw, Lalpa panpih in a thutiem uh nit di'n,
 Chawnban kiluoia a thutiem uh;
 Vang hun pien la, chang bang damin,
 A sietlei hinkhuou gui bang sau hen.

[V3]
 2. A thutiem uh nit din lunggil dik tak hun pien la,
 Kihehpih a ki-enkawl tuoh di'n;
 Phungbang vukin, vawn zatam chawi din,
 Damsunga Lal nasema kimang di'n,
 Nang vawp inla pui zelin.

[V4]
 3. Chung Pathien min loa, kitiem in a kigawm tau,
 Sam gi bang kikhen kit talo din;
 A nuom a haka kipanpih di'n,
 A kithutiem nau suguitung dingin,
 Lal Pathien in umsak hen.

[V5]
 4. Zie kichenna hi Lalpa Nangin hetpih inla,
 Krista leh Sapchuom etsak dik di'n,
 Na min lopina hung hi hen la,
 Sietlei hinkhuo beihman A chung u ah,
 Chung sunni bangin vakin.</lyrics>
</song>